Nordock is a land falling under a shadow. Dark forces struggle with the light, seeking to overcome all that is good and just.
Come in and adventure...
Slay the forces of evil.
Be an evil Drow yourself and fight against the light.
Become a master of a trade skill.
Or just sit with a good ale and tell tales to your companions.
Original mod from Richterms Retreat, modified by the nwn community. Improved and expanded further by EagleC on behalf of playZen. Contact: www.playzen.net / forums Nordock-playzen[v.1.0.6]
